metadata.description: Any holder of a 'Plug' , will have the ability to redeem the plug in exchange for advertising time in various areas of MetaSuites. For example when our Lobby is launched, a person could redeem the plug at various TV screens to schedule time to display/promote anything they want. You could also redeem your plug at the main stage in order to schedule time on the main stage of the lobby. Learn more at plug.meta-suites.io
